---

### Page Breakdown

#### Landing Page (`/`)
- **Hero**: Full-viewport animated gradient + floating destination cards
- **Search bar**: Centered, natural language with autocomplete
- **Feature grid**: 6 animated cards for each capability (flights, hotels, cars, transit, currency, tips)
- **Popular destinations**: Horizontal carousel with images and "from RM X" pricing
- **How it works**: 3-step animated flow

#### Results Page (`/results?q=...`)
- **Journey Strip** (horizontal timeline):
  ```
  ✈️ FLIGHTS → 🚗 CAR RENTAL → 🚇 TRANSIT → 🏨 HOTELS → 🔄 RETURN
  ```
- Each section expands to show full comparison data
- **Floating "Door-to-Door" cost bar** at bottom
- Side panel: Arrival card info + currency tips

#### Destination Page (`/destination/[slug]`)
- Deep-dive into a specific destination
- Tabs: Transit Map · Arrival Card · Currency & Payment · Travel Tips
- Interactive transit map (Leaflet.js)
- Full arrival card requirements
- Complete payment method guide

---

### Design System

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--bg-primary` | `#070b1a` | Page background |
| `--bg-surface` | `#0f1629` | Card backgrounds |
| `--bg-glass` | `rgba(15,22,41,0.7)` | Glassmorphism panels |
| `--accent-primary` | `#4f7df9` | Primary actions, links |
| `--accent-secondary` | `#7c5cfc` | Secondary highlights |
| `--accent-coral` | `#ff6b6b` | Alerts, price drops |
| `--accent-gold` | `#ffd166` | Stars, ratings, savings |
| `--accent-green` | `#36d399` | Cheapest price, success |
| `--text-primary` | `#f0f2f5` | Main text |
| `--text-secondary` | `#8892a8` | Muted text |
| `--glass-blur` | `blur(20px)` | Backdrop filter |
| `--radius-md` | `12px` | Card border radius |
| `--radius-lg` | `20px` | Large card radius |
| `--transition` | `0.3s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1)` | Smooth transitions |

- **Typography**: Inter (body) + Outfit (headings) via `next/font`
- **Dark mode by default** — premium travel aesthetic
- **Glassmorphism** cards with subtle borders
- **Micro-animations**: Hover lifts, gradient shifts, staggered scroll reveals
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first at 375px, tablet 768px, desktop 1200px

---

### Mock Data Scope

| Data Type | Volume | Details |
|-----------|--------|---------|
| Destinations | 6 | Tokyo, Seoul, Bangkok, Bali, London, Istanbul |
| Airlines | 8+ | AirAsia, MAS, JAL, Korean Air, Scoot, Emirates, Thai Airways, Singapore Airlines |
| Flights per route | 8-10 | Varied prices, durations, layovers |
| Hotels per destination | 5 | Each with prices from 6 platforms |
| Car rental providers | 4 | Hertz, Avis, Budget, local providers |
| Transit systems | Per city | MRT/subway lines, airport express, bus routes |
| Arrival card fields | Per country | Visa, health, customs, digital forms |
| Currency info | Per country | Exchange rate, payment methods, ATM info, tips |
| Travel tips | 15-20 per destination | Visa, weather, culture, safety, money, events |

